sentence: The war cry for justice was all over - Much to the chagrin of the authorities.
Danish: Krigskriget for retfærdighed var helt over - meget til myndighedens chagrin.
backtrans: The cry of justice was completely above - much to the authority's chagrin.

sentence: The regime's decision adumbrates the underlying agenda.
Danish: Regimets beslutning adumbrater den underliggende dagsorden.
backtrans: The regime's decision Adumbrates the underlying agenda.

sentence: The community was anxious over the passing of the much needed reforms.
Danish: Fællesskabet var ivrig over overførslen af de meget nødvendige reformer.
backtrans: The Community was eager about the transfer of the very necessary reforms.

sentence: The think tank  published a paper outlining their apology of capital punishment.
Danish: Tænkbeholderen offentliggjorde et papir, der beskriver deres undskyldning for dødsstraf.
backtrans: The think tank published a paper describing their apology for the death penalty.

sentence: Aught was left of the petition's validity
Danish: Aught blev efterladt af andragendets gyldighed
backtrans: Aught was left by the validity of the petition

sentence: The President exhorted his ministers to buckle up as key opposition support for his economic plan was about to buckle.
Danish: Præsidenten formandede sine ministre til at spænde op som nøglepositionsstøtte til sin økonomiske plan var ved at spænde.
backtrans: The President President its ministers to buckle up as key position support for its economic level was by buckle.

sentence: The voters were chuffed to see the bill passed.
Danish: Vælgerne blev chuffed for at se regningen bestået.
backtrans: The voters were chuffed to see the bill passed.

sentence: The lawyer's discursive narration swayed the jury.
backtrans: The lawyer's discursive tale swayed the jury.

sentence: The EU block opposed an eventual imposition of anti-dumping measures.
Danish: EU-blokken modsatte sig en eventuel indførelse af antidumpingforanstaltninger.
backtrans: The EU block opposes any imposition of anti-dumping measures.

sentence: A fulsome eulogy was delivered by the sly counsel.
Danish: En Fulsome Eulogy blev leveret af Sly Counsel.
backtrans: A fully eulogy was supplied by Sly Counsel.

sentence: The gig-economy agency decided to garnish the refunds!

sentence: Members of the anti-theocratic revolutionary movement overthrew the peers in power!

backtrans: Members of the anti-denocratic revolutionary movement overthrow peers in power!

sentence: The traitors disappointingly decided to fight with the colonialists.
Danish: Forræderne besluttede sig skuffende at kæmpe med kolonialisterne.
backtrans: The traitors decided disappointing to fight with the colonialists.
